rows.label: qev041403_MSG0001
rows.name: Pisa is late... What is she doing?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041403_MSG0002
rows.name: Hmm? Friend is gofer for Ngogo?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041403_MSG0003
rows.name:
Fine, whatever. Getting flung here has left Popote
too hungry to move.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041403_MSG0004
rows.name:
Bring coldberries at once! And spicy sacrifole pollen to
go with it, obviously.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041404_SEL0011
rows.name: Agree to find food for Popote.

rows.label: qev041404_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Popote to find his own food.

rows.label: qev041403_MSG0005
rows.name:
Friend is pleasantly obedient! Maybe once we get back
to caravan, Popote will have friend serve as adjunct
instead of Pisa.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041403_MSG0006
rows.name:
It best not to anger Popote when hungry, friend.
Now hurry up and fetch food![ST:wait ]
